section.section:
The staff shall include:
1 chief medical examiner;
2 deputy chief medical examiners;
Assistant medical examiners;
1 chief State toxicologist, 1 deputy chief State toxicologist, lead toxicologists, and assistant toxicologists;
1 serologist;
4 resident medical doctors who are training in forensic pathology;
1 chief forensic investigator, 2 deputy chief forensic investigators, lead forensic investigators, and assistant forensic investigators; and
1 autopsy services supervisor, 1 deputy supervisor, lead autopsy technicians, and assistant autopsy technicians.
